title: Interested in being apart of a Youtube video?

embed.description: Hello guys and welcome to my youtube channel. I am a Freelance League of Legends coach and also taking on a new mantle of youtuber. You can check out my cont...

body:
Hey people I am looking to start doing coaching content on my Youtube. But getting actual content is hard.
So for anyone out there who wants to get coached hit me up.
Either through Youtube or Twitter (There is also an email as well).  Friendlist is full on client so may not get your adds.

Coaching is free as long as you agree for me to post the content online. And also if you're a good sport as well.

So if your interested let me know.

replies.body: Hey hit me up on my email to get my skype address, would be beneficial if you had recorded videos of your gameplay but just answering pure questions is also possible.
I don't play very often, suck at this game and don't use any voice chat but I'd be interested
Having a holding two way convo is much enjoyable to the viewer so if your able to use voice chat would be best.
LOL I don't follow what you are on about.
If something like that really triggers you that much you might want to get off the internet
